In ''[[NetHack]]'', the letter '''H''' serves the following purposes:

* {{white|h}} represents a [[Humanoid (monster class)|humanoid]]:
** {{monsymlink|hobbit}}
** {{monsymlink|dwarf}}
** {{monsymlink|bugbear}}
** {{monsymlink|dwarf lord}}
** {{monsymlink|dwarf king}}
** {{monsymlink|mind flayer}}
** {{monsymlink|master mind flayer}}

* {{white|H}} represents a [[giant humanoid]]:
** {{monsymlink|giant}}
** {{monsymlink|stone giant}}
** {{monsymlink|hill giant}}
** {{monsymlink|fire giant}}
** {{monsymlink|frost giant}}
** {{monsymlink|storm giant}}
** {{monsymlink|ettin}}
** {{monsymlink|titan}}
** {{monsymlink|minotaur}}
** {{monsymlink|Cyclops}}

* It is also used as a [[direction]] key if [[numpad]] movement is off:
** Press {{kbd|h}} to move west.
** Press {{kbd|shift|h}} to move far west.

* If numpad movement is on:
** Pressing {{kbd|h}} opens the help menu.

==Variants==
===SLASH'EM===
[[SLASH'EM]] introduces new monsters that use the {{white|h}} and {{white|H}} glyphs:

* {{white|h}} humanoid:
** {{monsymlink|dwarf thief}}
** {{monsymlink|duergar}}
** {{monsymlink|deep one}}
** {{monsymlink|deeper one}}
** {{monsymlink|deepest one}}
* {{white|H}} giant humanoid:
** {{monsymlink|The Largest Giant}}

===UnNetHack===
[[UnNetHack]] introduces one new creature that use the {{white|h}} glyph:

* {{white|h}} humanoid:
** {{magenta|h}} [[Cthulhu]]
